-- A3 toposort on a BOUNDED pos array (permutation of 0..3). Edge
-- endpoints are carried as two coindexed seqs (efrom,eto) because
-- record-field access on a Seq element does not compile today (see
-- catalog C/A gap note). DAG 0→2, 1→3 has a topo order → exit 0.
-- entry: main
-- expect: exit = 0
import "stdlib/kernel.ev"
claim main
    pos ∈ Seq(Int)
    #pos = 4
    ∀ i ∈ {0..3} : 0 ≤ pos[i] ∧ pos[i] ≤ 3
    distinct(pos)
    efrom ∈ Seq(Int) = ⟨0, 1⟩
    eto   ∈ Seq(Int) = ⟨2, 3⟩
    ∀ (u, v) ∈ coindexed(efrom, eto) : pos[u] < pos[v]
    effects ∈ Seq(Effect) = ⟨Exit(0)⟩
